German Report Sees Flaws in Taxation of Company Cars, FTD Says

-- B y   A n g e l a   C u l l e n
-- 
2011-05-03T07:33:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-03/german-report-sees-flaws-in-taxation-of-company-cars-ftd-says.html
Laws governing the taxation of company
cars in Germany amount to a subsidization of vehicles that harm
the environment and deny the government as much as 5 billion
euros ($7.4 billion) in  tax revenue , Financial Times Deutschland
reported, citing a report commissioned by the environment
ministry.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
